sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A1 as Agent 1
    participant A2 as Agent 2
    participant FE1 as Angular UI - Agent 1
    participant FE2 as Angular UI - Agent 2
    participant API as Orders API
    participant UC as UpdateOrderUseCase
    participant Repo as Order Repository

    A1->>FE1: Opens order 1001
    FE1->>API: GET /api/v1/orders/1001
    API->>Repo: Load order
    Repo-->>API: Order version 1
    API-->>FE1: 200 OK with version 1

    A2->>FE2: Opens order 1001
    FE2->>API: GET /api/v1/orders/1001
    API->>Repo: Load order
    Repo-->>API: Order version 1
    API-->>FE2: 200 OK with version 1

    A1->>FE1: Changes delivery address
    FE1->>API: PUT /api/v1/orders/1001 with version 1
    API->>UC: Update order command
    UC->>Repo: Compare submitted version 1 with current version 1
    Repo-->>UC: Version matches
    UC->>Repo: Persist changes and increment to version 2
    API-->>FE1: 200 OK with version 2

    A2->>FE2: Changes internal comment
    FE2->>API: PUT /api/v1/orders/1001 with stale version 1
    API->>UC: Update order command
    UC->>Repo: Compare submitted version 1 with current version 2
    Repo-->>UC: Version mismatch
    UC-->>API: OrderConflictException
    API-->>FE2: 409 Conflict with current order snapshot
    FE2-->>A2: Shows conflict feedback without overwriting data
